---
import LegalLayout from '~/layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { BRAND_NAME, BRAND_LEGAL_NAME, CONTACT_EMAIL } from '~/data/site';
---

<LegalLayout routeKey="privacy">
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how {BRAND_LEGAL_NAME} ("we", "us", "{BRAND_NAME}")
    collects, uses, shares and protects your personal data when you visit
    fairledger.io or interact with our products. We comply with the UK GDPR, the EU
    GDPR, the Data Protection Act 2018 and PIPEDA where applicable.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
  <p>We collect three categories of personal data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Information you give us</strong> - your email address when you
      contact us, sign in or sign up for the wager-share program.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Information collected automatically</strong> - your IP address
      (truncated to /24 within 24 hours), the page you viewed, the page that
      referred you and your user agent. We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party
      analytics scripts. Server logs are retained for 30 days for security.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>On-chain transaction data</strong> - when we attribute a payout to
      your wallet for the wager-share program, we record only the wallet address
      and amount, not your name or email.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Why we use your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To reply to questions you submit through the contact form.</li>
    <li>To deliver wager-share rewards you have earned.</li>
    <li>To prevent abuse, fraud and bot scraping of our data feeds.</li>
    <li>To produce aggregate, anonymised traffic statistics.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Lawful basis</h2>
  <p>
    We rely on (a) <strong>contract</strong> performance for wager-share payouts,
    (b) <strong>legitimate interests</strong> for security logs and product
    analytics and (c) <strong>consent</strong> for any marketing email you opt
    into. You may withdraw consent at any time without affecting prior processing.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Who we share data with</h2>
  <p>We use a small set of vetted processors:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> - CDN, hosting, DDoS protection (UK / EU regions).</li>
    <li><strong>Stripe</strong> - if you ever pay us, payment processing only.</li>
    <li><strong>Google Workspace</strong> - email delivery for the contact form.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do not sell personal data to anyone, ever. Operators referenced on the
    site receive only your sign-up referral - they do not receive your email or
    any FairLedger account data.
  </p>

  <h2>5. International transfers</h2>
  <p>
    Some processors are based in the United States. Where data leaves the UK or
    the EEA, we rely on the UK International Data Transfer Addendum and the EU
    Standard Contractual Clauses (June 2021).
  </p>

  <h2>6. Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Server logs: 30 days.</li>
    <li>Wager-share payout records: 7 years (UK financial-records law).</li>
    <li>Contact-form messages: 18 months from last reply, then deleted.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Your rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
    <li>Correct inaccurate data.</li>
    <li>Erase your data ("right to be forgotten").</li>
    <li>Restrict or object to processing.</li>
    <li>Receive your data in a portable format.</li>
    <li>Lodge a complaint with the UK Information Commissioner's Office (ico.org.uk).</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Exercise any of these by emailing <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
    We respond within 30 days.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    See our <a href="/cookies/">cookie policy</a> for the full list of cookies we
    set, their purpose and how to disable them.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    We will post material updates here at least 30 days before they take effect
    and email registered users.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
